videos.description: Josiah-Jordan James knocks down his third 3-pointer of the game, forcing Memphis to take a timeout.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (James hyped after knocking down his third 3) 2019/12/14

videos.headline: James hyped after knocking down his third 3

videos.description: Precious Achiuwa hauls in the rebound and throws down the two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Achiuwa gets the and-1 dunk

videos.description: Tyler Harris spins and scores, giving Memphis a one-point lead over Tennessee at the half.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Harris beats the buzzer to give Memphis the lead) 2019/12/14

videos.headline: Harris beats the buzzer to give Memphis the lead

videos.description: Yves Pons rises high for the block, leading to a Jordan Bowden transition layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Pons' block leads to a Bowden layup) 2019/12/14

videos.headline: Pons' block leads to a Bowden layup

videos.description: Damion Baugh drains the 3-pointer, giving Memphis a 2-point lead with under two minutes left.
videos.headline: Baugh knocks down clutch 3

videos.description: Memphis is able to outlast Tennessee in the final seconds to break the Volunteers' long winning streak at home.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (Memphis ends Tennessee’s 31-game home winning streak) 2019/12/14 SOTFULL

videos.headline: Memphis ends Tennessee's 31-game home winning streak
